data.description: Fantastic Terrace Heights rambler boasts three bedrooms, great primary suite with a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. The other two bedrooms are generously sized and share a full bathroom. The living spaces are bright and open, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. The kitchen features ample counter and storage space, as well as a breakfast bar. Outside, the backyard offers privacy and a peaceful setting, with valley views adding to the tranquility. This home also includes a two-car garage and is located on a quiet cul de sac, providing a quiet environment. With a two-year-old roof and furnace, this home offers worry-free ownership. Don't miss out on the opportunity to tour this fantastic home.
